	(gr_text "Recommended:\n- 2oz copper\n- U1: TPS54560\n- U4/U5: TC4427\n- U6: XT9080\n- U9: CH224K\n- Q2-Q5: IRLB3813\n- D1: MBR20045CT Schottky Diode\n- L1: 1040 22uG inductor\n- J10-J13: MKDS 5mm terminals\n- D4-D7: Optional fly-back diode\n  MBRB2045CT (Schottky)"
